We have rejected the negotiation proposals. The Left shows their gratituge, whilst the labor and reformist wings accuse us of inaction in the face of an exisential threat towards Germany. The far-right uses this as an opportunity to show the weakness in our republic, shaking the public's belief quite a bit.


